verse.lines:
{lang-eng}Amazing words!—He ’gave Himself for me,’
For me—rebellious, sinful, guilty me.
For me the Savior bore the cross and shame;
Rejoice, my soul, and bless His sacred name.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}For me He was reviled, despised, betrayed;
For me was scourged, condemned and crucified;
For me He suffered on th’ accursed tree,
For me—lost, wretched, vile, unworthy me.{/lang-eng}
